messages.message: Working on an HSBC demo for tommorow and its been a long time since I built a metaflow binary to run but forgot how weird the process is, you all may know this already... but just want to repoint out.

First you have to open flow where all the flows reside. Second create metaflow (which creates an internal folder and brings you to JSON code). Third go back and reopen the workflow folder, run compile and point at the metaflow file and classifier, compile. Lastly reopen flow again, click run and choose binary, etc.
